06:03.400 --> 06:07.791
- It's here! The body’s here!
- Where? Where?

06:38.520 --> 06:40.397
“NEPHEW IN-SU”

06:49.400 --> 06:51.391
Yeah, this is your uncle.

06:51.400 --> 06:55.393
What are you doing? Watching TV again?

06:56.280 --> 07:00.671
What... what am I doing?
Well, I’m always studying.

07:01.120 --> 07:03.031
You know that thing these days...

07:03.520 --> 07:05.351
The Tripitaka Koreana into Latin...

07:05.360 --> 07:07.999
I’m translating it now.

07:08.280 --> 07:10.430
What’s wrong? Got something to say?

07:10.440 --> 07:14.274
Uncle, I think I’ll go live with you.

07:16.720 --> 07:17.869
What? Why?

07:17.880 --> 07:19.552
What... what’s wrong?

07:19.560 --> 07:23.439
Well... l feel a bit lonely and

07:24.920 --> 07:26.717
