that I’m transferring.

07:59.720 --> 08:00.914
Now, why would you decide

08:00.920 --> 08:03.832
that on your own?

08:04.080 --> 08:07.117
As lame as I may be,
I’m still your uncle. Your uncle!

08:09.080 --> 08:11.310
Anyway, you’re living in my parents’ house.

08:13.520 --> 08:16.876
Yeah, well... that’s true, but...

08:18.320 --> 08:19.435
By any chance...

08:20.120 --> 08:25.319
did you hear anything
about A-young’s family?

08:25.440 --> 08:27.192
Who? A-young?

08:27.400 --> 08:31.313
You mean, that incident
when you were in elementary school?

08:31.960 --> 08:34.519
That was a long time ago.

08:34.520 --> 08:36.556
