Look how he's playing the innocent!

17:31.400 --> 17:32.879
Fuck!

17:35.040 --> 17:36.439
I’m talking about Hyun-jig.

17:38.040 --> 17:39.553
I’m not interested in her.

17:39.880 --> 17:41.313
Not interested?

17:44.640 --> 17:46.153
You asshole!

17:46.640 --> 17:51.111
You’re not interested? No?
No? Not interested? Fuck!

17:56.040 --> 17:57.234
You’re not interested?

17:57.360 --> 17:59.157
