the big city?

18:06.360 --> 18:08.635
Get out of my way! Fuck!

18:08.640 --> 18:10.153
Wanna know what I hate the most?

18:10.560 --> 18:12.073
Squabbling! You bastard!

18:22.000 --> 18:23.353
Hey, KANG In-su!

18:24.720 --> 18:25.550
