18:25.560 --> 18:28.199
Yeolsung Elementary School.
Remember A-young?

18:30.720 --> 18:31.789
KANG In-su!

18:31.800 --> 18:34.837
- A-young keeps talking to you?
- The missing kid?

18:34.840 --> 18:37.229
She says she can’t breathe underwater.

18:37.240 --> 18:39.708
- You shouldn’t lie like that.
- If you keep lying...

18:39.720 --> 18:41.995
It’s true! A-young’s right here!

18:43.720 --> 18:45.631
Where did this water come from?

18:46.160 --> 18:47.718
Can’t breathe. I can’t breathe.

18:47.720 --> 18:48.550
I can’t breathe!

18:48.560 --> 18:49.560
I can’t breathe!!

18:52.560 --> 18:55.552
I don’t want ghost-ridden kid hanging
around Hyun-ji.

18:58.760 --> 19:02.275
So, you better lie low and don’t make me
spread rumors about you.

19:27.440 --> 19:29.635
“CHORONG”

19:32.840 --> 19:36.355
Yeah, mom. Just got out.

19:37.440 --> 19:39.192
Did you find Chorong?

19:39.720 --> 19:42.553
Did you really lose him?

19:43.080 --> 19:44.080
Whatever. Bye.

20:11.280 --> 20:12.554
What the...

20:14.520 --> 20:15.396
Fuck!

20:15.400 --> 20:18.392
You bitches fucking scared me!

20:18.400 --> 20:20.868
You act all stuck up but you’re such
a scaredy-cat.

20:20.880 --> 20:22.598
Bullshit. When was I?

20:22.600 --> 20:24.989
Then, why’d you get all jumpy like
a crazy bitch?

20:25.320 --> 20:26.514
Don’t know...

20:27.720 --> 20:28.720
Let’s go.

22:04.680 --> 22:05.680
Where are you?!

22:05.760 --> 22:08.877
Who the fuck are you? Come out!

22:10.600 --> 22:12.272
Come on out!

22:30.040 --> 22:31.792
- What?
- Na-ra...

22:33.040 --> 22:34.951
That bitch is here!

22:35.120 --> 22:37.793
Sae-hee is... Sae-hee!

22:37.800 --> 22:39.358
What? Who’s there?

22:40.080 --> 22:42.355
I can’t hear you. Speak up.

22:45.040 --> 22:47.759
Hey, Sung-hee!

22:48.440 --> 22:50.954
Hello? Hello?

22:53.120 --> 22:57.033
Hey, Sung-hee. Say it again. Huh?

22:58.400 --> 22:59.549
Hello?

23:01.040 --> 23:02.393
Hello?

23:03.800 --> 23:04.949
Hello?

23:12.960 --> 23:14.359
Wait. Come over here.

23:14.640 --> 23:16.278
Why? Why, Hae-chul?

23:16.520 --> 23:20.638
Does this hurt? Or this? Or this?

23:21.360 --> 23:22.918
- They all hurt...
- Oh, then...

23:22.920 --> 23:25.036
- The second one hurts more...
- Get up. Get up.

23:27.640 --> 23:31.235
I think Sung-hee’s ran away again.
She didn't get home yesterday.

23:31.800 --> 23:33.597
- Again?
- Yeah.

23:34.120 --> 23:37.908
How come she runs away like
she’s just going out for a walk?

23:38.640 --> 23:41.074
Hae-chul!(Porn... porn!)

23:53.160 --> 23:55.390
Hey, you mutt! Go fetch the ball!

23:55.600 --> 23:58.637
Come on. Kick the ball right.

24:00.720 --> 24:02.676
I know you can see me.

24:02.680 --> 24:04.272
At the bus stop, the guide dog!

24:04.720 --> 24:06.120
Are you gonna keep acting that way?

24:07.720 --> 24:10.951
Wow. You’re totally ignoring me...

24:13.120 --> 24:15.395
I won’t ask you to relieve any grudges.

24:15.920 --> 24:16.636
Really?

24:16.720 --> 24:18.756
How mean of you!

24:19.440 --> 24:22.000
Do you think I’m talking
to you because I like you?

24:22.080 --> 24:25.152
I’m bored and I’ve no other choice...

24:25.520 --> 24:26.748
but to talk to you...

24:30.800 --> 24:32.028
Did you go to this school?

24:33.760 --> 24:34.988
I don’t know.

24:35.960 --> 24:37.313
I can’t really remember...

24:37.880 --> 24:40.189
whether I did or not.

24:41.280 --> 24:43.191
Don’t even know my name.

24:44.160 --> 24:45.639
Maybe it’s because I’m a ghost?

24:46.520 --> 24:47.999
Just because I was nice to you,

24:48.000 --> 24:49.360
you think we’re on the same level?

24:51.080 --> 24:53.320
If you want to die,
just keep trying to walk all over me.

24:55.080 --> 24:56.593
Why don’t you do something?

24:56.760 --> 24:58.796
He’s getting beat up for no reason.

25:11.240 --> 25:14.312
Hush! It’s the Mask!

25:32.760 --> 25:34.398
Shit. That was embarrassing.

25:35.000 --> 25:36.718
Well, no one’s around...

26:22.320 --> 26:23.833
So dusty...

27:24.880 --> 27:26.677
These two are a pair.

27:26.680 --> 27:28.910
When the sword gets under the spell,

27:28.920 --> 27:32.230
it’s set that this dagger gets under
the spell, too.

27:33.600 --> 27:37.434
Why care so much
about what a ghost said to you?

27:38.080 --> 27:40.036
But, she was right.

27:40.640 --> 27:41.709
Oh, geez.

27:43.560 --> 27:46.711
Whether a friend gets bullied or beat up,

27:46.800 --> 27:48.233
they don’t care.

27:50.440 --> 27:51.634
Me, neither...

27:54.280 --> 27:59.559
Well, it wasn’t like that
when I was in school.

28:00.520 --> 28:03.353
If a friend in my class got beat up,

28:03.360 --> 28:06.079
I stepped in to help the friend.

28:06.080 --> 28:09.277
I firmly handled such a
situation, as I recall.

28:10.400 --> 28:11.400
That’s how I remember it.

28:12.280 --> 28:13.395
You don’t believe me.

28:14.280 --> 28:18.239
Yeah, you don’t have to believe me.
You really don’t.

28:24.800 --> 28:26.233
Legs, do the split!

28:29.000 --> 28:31.195
One, two

28:31.880 --> 28:34.348
If I told the truth back then...

28:40.400 --> 28:44.996
A-young’s perpetrator would’ve
been caught much earlier, for sure.

28:45.640 --> 28:52.591
Anyway, it’s good that he did get caught.

28:52.760 --> 28:57.515
And, you were also the victim, right?

29:02.320 --> 29:07.917
Because of that,
you had to leave your hometown.

29:21.040 --> 29:22.234
Who are you?

29:28.200 --> 29:32.273
Yes! Moongchi has a scar on the front paw.

29:32.280 --> 29:33.269
“MOONGCHI”

29:33.280 --> 29:35.360
It also has a name tag
with ‘Moongchi’ written on it.

29:37.360 --> 29:41.114
Is my Moongchi really here?

29:43.080 --> 29:46.436
Yes, quietly sitting by your feet.

29:47.880 --> 29:50.440
No, a bit more to the left!

29:52.600 --> 29:54.591
Your girlfriend was here, too?

29:56.000 --> 29:58.753
Can you... hear my voice?

29:58.760 --> 30:01.194
Of course. I hear you very well.

30:02.640 --> 30:05.154
Why? Should I not hear you?

30:05.680 --> 30:08.319
No! You should. Of course.

30:08.520 --> 30:11.637
If you don’t believe me, you don’t have to.

30:11.960 --> 30:13.678
No! I believe you.

30:17.240 --> 30:18.912
I want to believe.

30:24.000 --> 30:28.073
So, A-young was the first
ghost you ever saw?

30:30.960 --> 30:31.870
Yeah.

30:31.880 --> 30:36.158
A-young... Iet's go home...

30:39.400 --> 30:44.190
No! No! No!

30:44.680 --> 30:48.912
She was in my class in elementary school.

30:49.760 --> 30:53.116
One day, she was found dead.

30:59.240 --> 31:00.639
A-young told me

31:00.640 --> 31:02.870
- Why arena’t you saying anything?
- about the perpetrator.

31:02.880 --> 31:07.635
- You said you knew, In-su.
- But, I lied.

31:08.360 --> 31:11.318
In-su. In-su.

31:13.400 --> 31:15.550
I’m not sure.

31:15.560 --> 31:19.348
I thought it’d get better
if I just left here.

31:23.080 --> 31:24.798
But, why did you come back?

31:26.160 --> 31:30.870
It felt like... A-young was waiting for me.

32:21.600 --> 32:22.635
Ex... Excuse me...

32:34.960 --> 32:36.075
Who are you?

32:38.400 --> 32:40.231
It’s not your fault.

32:40.800 --> 32:43.075
You even helped find A-young.

32:43.960 --> 32:47.919
Thanks for remembering and dropping by.

33:12.680 --> 33:14.432
Over there...

33:47.320 --> 33:51.074
A-young must've been waiting for you.

34:24.159 --> 34:25.878
Now...

34:27.600 --> 34:30.239
I feel a bit relieved.

35:13.080 --> 35:14.080
Your hands...

35:14.760 --> 35:15.760
Put them here.

35:34.760 --> 35:38.673
That’s strange... My
hands really feel warm.

35:40.440 --> 35:41.919
Really?

36:39.040 --> 36:40.837
School life's good for you these days?

36:44.040 --> 36:45.109
What?

36:47.040 --> 36:48.917
Embarrassed to get hit by a girl?

36:49.120 --> 36:50.348
Makes you mad?

36:52.080 --> 36:53.274
Getting on your nerves?

36:55.560 --> 36:57.676
Feeling angry and annoyed?

36:59.040 --> 37:01.838
Better let that hand go
if you don’t want to die.

37:04.400 --> 37:05.400
Stop it.

37:07.600 --> 37:09.875
You dick! I told you to
let go of that hand!

37:10.640 --> 37:11.755
Why are you butting in?

37:14.960 --> 37:16.757
Because you’re bullying for no reason!

37:26.560 --> 37:28.278
What a dork!

37:30.400 --> 37:31.515
Let’s go.

37:32.400 --> 37:33.913
Idiots.

38:26.920 --> 38:31.596
Come on out. I know. So, come out.

39:08.640 --> 39:09.709
“MURDER OF WOMAN
IN HER THIRTIES”

39:09.720 --> 39:11.153
On the 23rd,
the crime scene inspection was held

39:11.160 --> 39:12.718
with Ms. HWANG’s murder suspect,
Mr. PARK.

39:12.720 --> 39:14.199
“MURDERED AND BURIED
AFTER 10 YEARS OF STALKING”

39:14.200 --> 39:18.557
PARK is accused of killing
and secretly burying Ms. HWANG

39:18.560 --> 39:20.869
after stalking her for 10 years.

39:21.000 --> 39:22.399
The police concludes it

39:22.400 --> 39:24.755
as an accidental crime of passion...

39:24.760 --> 39:25.875
The mask...

39:25.880 --> 39:28.110
and will wrap up the case.

39:28.120 --> 39:29.075
People looking over the scene...

39:29.080 --> 39:30.433
So noisy! Really!

39:34.880 --> 39:39.078
How can I help you if
you don’t say anything?

39:39.840 --> 39:41.796
Say something. Say it!

39:43.120 --> 39:45.111
How could a ghost lack so much confidence?

